 control panel of the ship. A holographic projection showed the time in extremely accurate incriments. &quot;Hmm, I've gotta calibrate the alarm system when I get back from work...&quot; John yawned as he zipped by. The air pod slowed to a glide. He was at the Cybertronix facility now. His ship slowly docked inside of a parking tube. John pressed a putton on his control panel, and the side of the pod opened up. He stepped out and closed the door. The pod was taken by robotic hands and rushed off to the parking vault. John took the elevator up to the 24th level, where his office was. &quot;Morning Steve,&quot; he said to a passing co-worker. He walked passed a few cubicles and turned into his office. &quot;Hello Mai,&quot; he said to her. She was typing away, while listening to the automatic message system.<br>
