<br>
AAAAAAAAAHH!!! CREATURES OF THE BLACK! INFAMOUS MINIATURE DEVILS, ALL CLAMMERING TOWARDS ME, BEGONE AAAAAAAAAAAAAHHHHHHHHHHH!<br>
<br>
Steve's hands dropped all the screens as he frantically brushed away a small, white fuzzy on his black suit. The black slacks were made of the most durable synthetic cloth and leather products created by the company, and repelled most dirt and airborne objects, but there was one ON HIM!! He attacked the fuzzy savagely, and deposited it in a small box, where he watched sedistically as the fuzzball fried. He took in every last detail of the exposure; the beginning, where he could nearly see the waves of heat shimmer, the bright flash of light, the fuzzy texture of the ball, and the way the smoke's lines intricately danced and interwined as they rose off the charred piece of fuzz. With a dark grin on his face, Steve could even make out words and symbols in the smoke, only because *He* could, though. Only *He* was could see the details. Only *He* could hear the vapors, because only *He* was great enough to understand.<br>
<br>
Smiling smugly with what the stream of smoke that was whisked out a suction tube had told him, Steve professionally picked up one screen out of the amassed jumble, and saw someone pocketing a few of the high-end market chips from the electronics section. Smiling that They had helped him again, Steve sounded the alarm, and the gaurd-bots quickly apprehended him. &quot;Have a *nice* day!&quot; the speakers boomed. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub95.ezboard.com/uparadisetheheretic.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Paradise the Heretic</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://Auction.2y.net/user/paradisetheheretic/paradise.jpg" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Mistress of Decay</span><br>  Posts: 230<br> <font color=#FF0000>(7/31/02 5:14 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub95.ezboard.com/ffantasystoriesforumfrm7.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=9.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://auction.2y.net/user/paradisetheheretic/paradise.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Sci-Fi</span><hr size=1> Mai taped her finger impatiently against the hard surface of her glass desk.  She watched as the progress bar slowly crept up.  Mai was currently downloading all the design specifications for Cybertronix's new war missles.  What Mai knew and very few cavilians knew was that Cybertronix was under licence by the goverment to design most of the high end artillery to proved for the war effort in the Americas.  Mai, profesional hacker that she was, had found a way to download the specifications which she planned to sell on the black market to the highest bidder.  As the progress bar hit 100%  a smile spread across her delicate features.  &quot;Perfect.&quot;  she purred. <p><b>Sinfuly Yours,<br>Paradise Perdu<br>"Les vrais paradis sont les paradis que'on a perdu."<b></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000