&quot;hmph, Robots...&quot; ~Soon enough the damn things will take over the world. It's bad enough they're all over the place. But feelings? That's a bit extreme... They're pieces of junk, slaves in a way. Why do they need to be able to expirence emotion? That is the only thing separating us from them. Well... that and organic flesh. heh~<br>
<br>
